&lt;p&gt;Join us if you thrive on cross‑functional collaboration, care about building the smartest NPCs and digital players, and want to shape how millions of players experience our worlds, and everywhere in between.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
